# Aurras Music Player

![Aurras](assests/aurras.png)

**AurrasðŸŽ§** is a high-end **command line music player** that offers a seamless music experience directly in your terminal. It combines powerful search capabilities with an elegant interface, allowing you to play any song without leaving your command line.

